name: Unique Butterfly Wedding Stationery x 50 Invites
description:
Beautiful and unique this is my Butterfly Range of Wedding Stationery The picture you can see is of the Invitation however there are other matching items available ie : save the date, invites day/evening , RSVP , Order of service , Menu's,  thankyou cards or notelets , favor boxes and place cards can also supply serviette rings. I also do table planners in the same design and I am sure I could fulfill any other requirements you may have. 

All Handmade by me for that extra personal touch I have been designing Wedding Stationery for about 2 yrs now and one thing I have learnt over that time is not one person wants the same Weddings are such a personal occassion and therefore I am open to any ideas and can customise any order for you and to suit your needs and budget.

Advice I have to any one who is getting married is choose your Wedding Stationery carefully as they are the first contact you will have with your guests and can refect the style you have planned for your special day, Its advisable to select all Wedding Stationery well in advance, remembering that Invitations should be sent Aprox 3 months before your wedding day, Once your order is placed it will take me between 2-3 weeks to complete (on average order size 50 to 100 items) If however you need your order quicker than this then please let me know and I will try and accommidate.

Please contact me for a no obligation quote 

Please note that the price is for 50 invites only please contact me for a price on the whole range if needed
